name: Every beginning has an end
description: This artwork was created to visualize the moment before Bigbang. There are some theories in which there is no beginning or end and that this moment of expansion and contraction of the universe has already happened several times. Are we in a moment of contraction of one or more Bigbangs, where in the current position we have the illusion that the universe is expanding? The question remains...
